isReflexive

public boolean isReflexive()
R(X,X) is a reflexive relation. Reflexive relations may be computed by the shard if these relations are entailed by the axioms of the ontology. It may be desirable to filter these at the presentation layer, in which case this test can be applied

Returns:
true if node is the same as target
